description:
Contents:
- Summer Wreath "[Wall] A sunflower wreath to remind one of the summer."
- Sunflower Wreath "[Wall] A summer wreath with a lavish sunflower arrangement."
- Sunflower Planter: Large "[Furniture ★★★] A planter with large Sunflowers growing in it."
- Sunflower Planter: Small "[Furniture ★] A planter with Sunflowers growing in it."
- Sunflower Vase: Large "[Tabletop ★★★] A vase containing an arrangement of large sunflowers."
- Sunflower Vase: Small "[Tabletop ★] A vase containing an arrangement of sunflowers."
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop (General Store in Yano Market) when you purchase it.
name: Sunflower Interiors Pack Set
